{"tid":2008443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德情報局揭秘：習近平親自要求譚德塞壓下疫情訊息","createTime":"2020-05-09T04:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T03:27:05.000Z","uid":193217,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b4eee9a66f1eb64684b020b8367b426caba3f46f","tid":2008443,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"〔中央社〕國際追究武漢肺炎疫情責任的聲浪不斷，德國情報單位指出，中國國家主席習近平親自要求世衛秘書長譚德塞淡化疫情的嚴重性，中國的隱匿造成全球至少損失一個月的時間抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n最新一期「明鏡周刊」（Der Spiegel）報導，根據德國聯邦情報局（BND）情資，中國國家主席習近平1月21日與世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）通話時，要求世衛不要發布病毒人傳人的訊息和延後全球大流行的警告。<br />\n<br />\n結果世衛沈默多天，直到1月底才宣布2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）是「國際關注的公共衛生緊急事件」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，西方國家普遍認為，如果不是中國隱瞞訊息，疫情會容易控制得多，德國聯邦情報局的結論是由於北京封鎖消息，全球平白損失4到6個禮拜的時間對抗病毒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159919&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7dxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=01124aee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159919&h=443b36b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159919</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南德日報（Suddeutsche Zeitung）報導，德國羅伯特．科赫研究所（Robert Koch Institute）的專家也確信，疫情爆發一開始中國提供的訊息就不完整，為有效防疫，這個全國公共衛生的主管機關只好向聯邦情報局求助。<br />\n<br />\n不過，被問到中國是否應該對疫情蔓延負責時，中國駐德國大使吳懇告訴明鏡周刊，中國的快速反應讓世界至少有6個禮拜的時間準備，可惜許多國家沒有利用，一些政治人物甚至說只是流行性感冒。<br />\n<br />\n針對各國呼籲組織獨立團隊調查病毒的起源，吳懇說，「中國對國際調查持開放態度」，不過，不應該一開始就把責任推給中國，用所謂的國際調查來找證據。<br />\n<br />\n吳懇說，調查病毒起源的工作應由學者來執行，不能被政治人物作為工具。"},{"pid":"2b9d64b1d1dea7c2f5bed0ac23ecf883683636c8","tid":2008443,"uid":21545,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"我都係而家先知阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b950cea8464961dbc71c3c2082aaccecbc5e3883","tid":2008443,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"談生菜 都係雞珍2.0"},{"pid":"9e30cc21b9afa0729ca25dc0af7d3f63be549e3b","tid":2008443,"uid":273218,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"支持樓主出D post<br />\n都係對準支共<br />\n但次次推唔起"},{"pid":"ccd3c958c2cd12ef1fc2e1ea91e565411c21f327","tid":2008443,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"咩要求<br />\n下令先啱"},{"pid":"9bde2c9c0603dae1a5e6467d1b6d8d2d9ff01a2d","tid":2008443,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e30cc21b9afa0729ca25dc0af7d3f63be549e3b","tid":2008443,"uid":273218,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"支持樓主出D post<br />\n都係對準支共<br />\n但次次推唔起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"咁一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac13ba688ce4af11eae877c9208c31a1a02e86a6","tid":2008443,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"歐美唔信我地香港民間, 又唔信台灣, <br />\n走去信中共, 都有幾分抵死."},{"pid":"a8582983cba730a3fca2b0df52599b9f662ff045","tid":2008443,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2b9d64b1d1dea7c2f5bed0ac23ecf883683636c8","tid":2008443,"uid":21545,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:02:34.000Z","msg":"我都係而家先知阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"你蝻嚟"},{"pid":"f477d736a0301c300971f22b322ad219041ecac5","tid":2008443,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"維尼直接出手整死幾十萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd31416a2ab04eb8852fe31bc99a57b94921f89","tid":2008443,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16be87d6b4da975512d35c4eeaa04dd2906f